#
# Custom headers
#
my_hdr X-Operating-System: `uname`
my_hdr X-Date: `date`

#
# headers order
#
ignore *
unhdr_order *
unignore  Date: From: Reply-To: Mail-Followup-To: To: Cc: Subject:
hdr_order Subject: From: To: Cc: Date: Reply-To: